Title : Oh! My Lady (K-Drama) (2010)
 
English Subtitles: Yes
Number of Episodes: 16
Width     : 624 pixels
Height    : 352 pixels

Date Aired (YYYY-MM-DD): 2010-Mar-22 to 2010-May-11
More Info: http://wiki.d-addicts.com/Oh!_My_Lady

Summary: A spunky 35-year-old housewife, Yoon Gae Hwa, takes on the job of manager to prickly top star Sung Min Woo in order to earn enough money to regain custody of her child from her ex-husband. Romantic hijinks and hilarity ensues when they find themselves in an awkward living situation as Min Woo pays Gae Hwa to take care of his daughter, Ye Eun.
